WEBVTT

00:07:29.065 --> 00:07:32.380
I firmly believe it's time
for us to rethink medicine.

00:07:32.885 --> 00:07:35.757
We must establish proactive
health-care technologies.

00:07:36.179 --> 00:07:39.024
A change must be brought out
not 10 years from now,

00:07:39.048 --> 00:07:40.347
not five years from now,

00:07:40.371 --> 00:07:41.526
but today.

00:07:41.550 --> 00:07:43.939
And so, hopefully, one day,

00:07:43.963 --> 00:07:45.729
with the help of these devices,

00:07:45.753 --> 00:07:50.265
someone else won't lose
his or her grandfather just like I did.

00:07:50.289 --> 00:07:51.539
Thank you so much.

00:07:51.563 --> 00:07:53.024
(Applause)

00:07:53.048 --> 00:07:54.921
Thank you.

00:07:54.945 --> 00:07:56.952
(Applause)

00:07:56.976 --> 00:07:58.126
Thank you.